<br>
The game does have some outstanding concepts though.  I really like the 3 different exp types (combat, exploration, and trade - each having it's own exp bar) and the exp debt.  When you die, instead of loosing exp, you are given an exp debt which you pay back with half the exp you earn until the debt is paid off. (No more loosing days worth of exp.)<br>
